description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Plezier purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 126, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Box for East, 2 for South, and Box for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70632-84244-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
